00111 struct GpsFixDataInt
00112 {
00113     UINT16          m_gps_week;
00114     UINT32          m_gps_tow;
00115     UINT16          m_microsec;
00116     UINT8           m_speed_valid;
00118     UINT32          m_speed;
00120     UINT32          m_hdop;
00122     UINT32          m_time_tag_delta;
00124     UINT32          m_loc_error;
00125     UINT8           m_num_sats;
00126     SatelliteInfo   m_sat_info[MAX_SATS];
00127 
00129     void Convert(GpsFixData& fix_data) const
00130     {
00131         fix_data.m_gps_week = m_gps_week;
00132         fix_data.m_gps_tow = m_gps_tow;
00133         fix_data.m_microsec = m_microsec;
00134         fix_data.m_speed_valid = m_speed_valid;
00135         fix_data.m_speed.m_mantissa = m_speed;
00136         const UINT16 c_exponent = 3; // As defined within Lcs stack
00137         if(m_speed > 0)
00138         {
00139             // Set the exponent to the hard-coded value
00140             fix_data.m_speed.m_exponent = c_exponent;
00141             
00142             // Convert the speed from knots to m/sec: 1 knot = 0.5144444444444 m/sec
00143             UnsignedValue conv_factor;
00144             conv_factor.m_mantissa = 5144; conv_factor.m_exponent = 4;
00145             fix_data.m_speed *= conv_factor;
00146         }
00147         else
00148         {
00149             fix_data.m_speed.m_exponent = 0;
00150         }
00151         fix_data.m_hdop.m_mantissa = m_hdop;
00152         fix_data.m_hdop.m_exponent = (m_hdop != 0) ? c_exponent : 0;
00153         fix_data.m_time_tag_delta = m_time_tag_delta;
00154         fix_data.m_loc_error.m_mantissa = m_loc_error;
00155         fix_data.m_loc_error.m_exponent = (m_loc_error != 0) ? c_exponent : 0;
00156         fix_data.m_num_sats = m_num_sats;
00157         memcpy(&fix_data.m_sat_info[0], &m_sat_info[0], sizeof(m_sat_info));
00158     }
00159 
00160 }; // GpsFixDataInt
